summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning; amending page 189 of the Official Land Use Map, Seattle Municipal Code Section 23.32.016 to rezone an area south of South Norfolk Street, west of Airport Way South, and east and north of the City boundary with the City of Tukwila from General Industrial 2 with an eighty-five foot height limit (IG-2/U-85) to Industrial Commercial with an eighty-five foot height limit (IC/U- 85).
